core: shadow core
all: workspace-level changes spanning multiple crates
tui: terminal interface & rendering
services: background services (ingest, watcher)
tools: llm-callable tools (search, fetch, weather)
continuity: belief persistence & mind schema
locus: session orchestration & chat flow
mind: belief extraction, updates & reflection
llmclient: llm client, streaming & provider routing
db: sqlite layer & query logic
utils: shared utilities & helpers
config: app configuration & paths
